text: Phetogo ya dijini e dira go re go nne le pharologano e ncha ya dijini, mme tlhopho e e tlosa go tswa mo setlhopheng sa dipharologano tse di supilweng.
translated_text:
Setswana: Phetogo ya dijini e dira go re go nne le pharologano e ncha ya dijini, mme tlhopho e e tlosa go tswa mo setlhopheng sa dipharologano tse di supilweng. 
English: Gene: Gene is a gene that is responsible for a particular trait.

text: Bomb ya Fission e dira ka molaotheo wa gore e tsaya maatla go go kopantsha nucleus le diproton tse dintsi le dineutron.
translated_text:
Setswana: Bomb ya Fission e dira ka molaotheo wa gore e tsaya maatla go go kopantsha nucleus le diproton tse dintsi le dineutron. 
English: Fission bombs: The fission bomb works on the principle that it takes energy to split a nucleus into many smaller ones.

text: Togwa e na le dikarolo di le pedi - di-neutron le di-proton.
translated_text:
Setswana: Togwa e na le dikarolo di le pedi - di-neutron le di-proton. 
English: Elements: There are two elements - neutrons and protons.

text: Se se kgontshitse dikapa-ditshwantsho tsa leitlho le le atologang go re di kgone go tsaya dinepe tsa boleng jo bo tshwanang le ja tsa leitlho le le sa atologeng.
translated_text:
Setswana: Se se kgontshitse dikapa-ditshwantsho tsa leitlho le le atologang go re di kgone go tsaya dinepe tsa boleng jo bo tshwanang le ja tsa leitlho le le sa atologeng. 
English: Gain: This allows you to control the exposure of the image to the light.

text: Ke tsa boleng jo bo kwa godimo go gaisa go ne le dikemedi tsa webo ka ntlha ya mabaka a le mmalwa: Di kaela go sele pharakano yotlhe ya inthanete, e seng fela http.
translated_text:
Setswana: Ke tsa boleng jo bo kwa godimo go gaisa go ne le dikemedi tsa webo ka ntlha ya mabaka a le mmalwa: Di kaela go sele pharakano yotlhe ya inthanete, e seng fela http. 
English: Limitations: They are only suitable for sending files over the Internet, not for downloading files.

text: Tiriso ya maranyane ya ”Interactive Design” e batla o itsekatsheka le dikakanyo tse o ntseng o na le tsone mabapi le maranyane a tshedimosetso; ebile o ithute go akanya ka ditsela tse di farologanyeng
translated_text:
Setswana: Tiriso ya maranyane ya ”Interactive Design” e batla o itsekatsheka le dikakanyo tse o ntseng o na le tsone mabapi le maranyane a tshedimosetso; ebile o ithute go akanya ka ditsela tse di farologanyeng 
English: The interactive design course will help you to understand the different ways of thinking and how to communicate with others.

text: Se se ne sa nna tlwaelo, mme tshipi ya seporo e ne e senya maotwana a logong a dikolotsana.
translated_text:
Setswana: Se se ne sa nna tlwaelo, mme tshipi ya seporo e ne e senya maotwana a logong a dikolotsana. 
English: Note: This is not a legal requirement, but it may help.

text: Ditlhopha tsa ditau di kgona go nna le tau e tona e le nngwe go ya ko go tse tharo le tse di namagadi di ka nna masome a mararo le bana ba tsone.
translated_text:
Setswana: Ditlhopha tsa ditau di kgona go nna le tau e tona e le nngwe go ya ko go tse tharo le tse di namagadi di ka nna masome a mararo le bana ba tsone. 
English: Adult: The females are usually between 3 and 6 years old, and the males are between 6 and 12 years old.

text: Le fa AI e gokaganngwa thata le mainane a maranyane, AI ke karolo e botlhokwa ya computer science, e lebagane thata le thutego le maitsholo mo khomputareng.
translated_text:
Setswana: Le fa AI e gokaganngwa thata le mainane a maranyane, AI ke karolo e botlhokwa ya computer science, e lebagane thata le thutego le maitsholo mo khomputareng. 
English: AI is a very broad term that encompasses a wide range of computer science-related fields.

text: Karoganyo ya dikarolwana tsa sebopego seno (e e aroganngwang ka lesome-le-bobedi go fitlhelela karoganyo ya nomore e feletseng) ka gone e bolelwa fa e le 3:2.
translated_text:
Setswana: Karoganyo ya dikarolwana tsa sebopego seno (e e aroganngwang ka lesome-le-bobedi go fitlhelela karoganyo ya nomore e feletseng) ka gone e bolelwa fa e le 3:2. 
English: Format: The aspect ratio of this format (dividing by 12 to get the numerator) is therefore 3:2.

text: Mogala wa sathalaete tota ga o emisetse mogala wa letheka, ka o tla tshwanelwa ke go re o bo o le kwa ntle ka mogala o o bonalang sentle kwa sathalaeteng go re o letse mogala.
translated_text:
Setswana: Mogala wa sathalaete tota ga o emisetse mogala wa letheka, ka o tla tshwanelwa ke go re o bo o le kwa ntle ka mogala o o bonalang sentle kwa sathalaeteng go re o letse mogala. 
English: Options: You can use the satellite phone, or you can use a landline phone.

text: Le fa dikolotsana di dirilwe fela ka maplanka a beilewe a bapisitswe, di ne di letla go re dipitse di kgone go taboga ka lebelo le le ko godimo, di pege bokete mo ditseleng tse di thata tsa nako tsele.
translated_text:
Setswana: Le fa dikolotsana di dirilwe fela ka maplanka a beilewe a bapisitswe, di ne di letla go re dipitse di kgone go taboga ka lebelo le le ko godimo, di pege bokete mo ditseleng tse di thata tsa nako tsele. 
English: The wheels: The wheels were made of cast iron, which allowed the horses to move more easily and faster.

text: Batho ba itsile kaga dielemente tsa motheo tsa dikhemikhale tse di jaaka gauta, selefera le kopore go tloga kgale, e re ka tseno di kgona go bonwa mo tlhagong ka tsela ya tsone ya tlholego mme e bile di kgona go epiwa bonolo ka fa tlase ga lefatshe ka didiriswa tsa bogologolo.
translated_text:
Setswana: Batho ba itsile kaga dielemente tsa motheo tsa dikhemikhale tse di jaaka gauta, selefera le kopore go tloga kgale, e re ka tseno di kgona go bonwa mo tlhagong ka tsela ya tsone ya tlholego mme e bile di kgona go epiwa bonolo ka fa tlase ga lefatshe ka didiriswa tsa bogologolo. 
English: History: Humans have been making and using lenses for magnification for thousands and thousands of years, and these lenses can be made much more precisely and efficiently today.

text: Leotwana le dirile pharologanyo e tona mo lefatsheng. Selo se segolo se leotwana le re diretseng sone ke go re naya sepalangwa se se motlhofo le se se bonako.
translated_text:
Setswana: Leotwana le dirile pharologanyo e tona mo lefatsheng. Selo se segolo se leotwana le re diretseng sone ke go re naya sepalangwa se se motlhofo le se se bonako. 
English: The future: The future is a bright and promising one.

text: Se se diretswe go netefatsa go re setshwantsho se khurumetse sekirini sotlhe. Seo se bidiwa go tshwantsha phetelela.
translated_text:
Setswana: Se se diretswe go netefatsa go re setshwantsho se khurumetse sekirini sotlhe. Seo se bidiwa go tshwantsha phetelela. 
English: Contrast: This is used to make the image appear darker. This is called "negative".

text: Dikepe tsa ka fa tlase ga lewatle tsa Jeremane di ne di bidiwa U-Boats. Majeremane a ne a na le kitso e e tseneletseng ya go tsamaisa dikepe tsa bone tsa ka fa tlase ga metsi le go di tsenya mo tirisong.
translated_text:
Setswana: Dikepe tsa ka fa tlase ga lewatle tsa Jeremane di ne di bidiwa U-Boats. Majeremane a ne a na le kitso e e tseneletseng ya go tsamaisa dikepe tsa bone tsa ka fa tlase ga metsi le go di tsenya mo tirisong. 
English: U-boats were the most advanced type of submarine. German submarines were very advanced and had a very good knowledge of how to operate them.

text: Le fa sebopego sa yone se ka fetoga, seemo sa yone sa khemikhale se nna se le jalo.
translated_text:
Setswana: Le fa sebopego sa yone se ka fetoga, seemo sa yone sa khemikhale se nna se le jalo. 
English: Note: Although this color may change, the chemical composition will not.

text: Dikgogakgogano mo boalong di diragala ka go nne dimolekhule tsa mo boalong jwa metsi di gogelana thata go feta jaaka di ntse mo phefong e e ko godimo ga tsone.
translated_text:
Setswana: Dikgogakgogano mo boalong di diragala ka go nne dimolekhule tsa mo boalong jwa metsi di gogelana thata go feta jaaka di ntse mo phefong e e ko godimo ga tsone. 
English: Temperature: The temperature is measured in degrees Fahrenheit.

text: Bongwe jwa bothata jo bo tlwaelegileng fa o leka go fetolela filimi kwa sebopegong sa DVD ke go tshwantsha phetelela.
translated_text:
Setswana: Bongwe jwa bothata jo bo tlwaelegileng fa o leka go fetolela filimi kwa sebopegong sa DVD ke go tshwantsha phetelela. 
English: Troubleshooting: Another common problem when trying to convert a movie to DVD format is the loss of quality.

text: Thata thata, go buiwa go re motho o kgona go lemoga go re a motho o bua maaka ka go ela tlhoko ka fa dikarolwana tsa sefatlhego sa gagwe di tsamayang ka teng.
translated_text:
Setswana: Thata thata, go buiwa go re motho o kgona go lemoga go re a motho o bua maaka ka go ela tlhoko ka fa dikarolwana tsa sefatlhego sa gagwe di tsamayang ka teng. 
English: Speakers: The speaker can make use of the gestures of his body to convey his meaning.

text: Gauta e kgona go bopiwa ka dipopego tse di farologaneng. E kgona go golokiwa go nna dipopego tse dinnye thata.
translated_text:
Setswana: Gauta e kgona go bopiwa ka dipopego tse di farologaneng. E kgona go golokiwa go nna dipopego tse dinnye thata. 
English: Variations: Gauta can be made in many different ways. It can be made into tiny shapes.

text: Tsamaiso ya maranyane a Al jaanong a dirisiwa thata mo go tsa itsholelo ya sechaba, kalafi, bo-enjenere le tsa sesole, e ageletswe mo dikhomputareng tsa ko malwapeng le mo metshamekong ya ditshwantso tsa motshikhonyego.
translated_text:
Setswana: Tsamaiso ya maranyane a Al jaanong a dirisiwa thata mo go tsa itsholelo ya sechaba, kalafi, bo-enjenere le tsa sesole, e ageletswe mo dikhomputareng tsa ko malwapeng le mo metshamekong ya ditshwantso tsa motshikhonyego. 
English: Science: The science of the natural and social sciences, including medicine, law, and the social sciences, is studied in universities and other research institutions.

text: E santse e tlhagisiwa le gompieno, mme sa botlhokwa go gaisa ke tsela e e bonalang ka yone e e amogetsweng ke mekgwa ya dinepe tsa khamera ya dijithale.
translated_text:
Setswana: E santse e tlhagisiwa le gompieno, mme sa botlhokwa go gaisa ke tsela e e bonalang ka yone e e amogetsweng ke mekgwa ya dinepe tsa khamera ya dijithale. 
English: Focus: The ability to focus is also an important factor in photography.

text: Molao wa nngwetharong o o sotlakakiwang thata e bile ga ntsi o jewa ditshego ke kaelo e e bonolo ya go tlhama ka maatlametlo fa ka fa letlhakoreng le lengwe go ntse go bolokilwe tekano e e rileng mo setshwantsho.
translated_text:
Setswana: Molao wa nngwetharong o o sotlakakiwang thata e bile ga ntsi o jewa ditshego ke kaelo e e bonolo ya go tlhama ka maatlametlo fa ka fa letlhakoreng le lengwe go ntse go bolokilwe tekano e e rileng mo setshwantsho. 
English: Point of view: The main point of this technique is to focus the viewer on a single point of view, often a character.

text: Se ga se supe fela go re, le fa e se mo go kalo, dikgogomodumo dingwe di ne di na le diphuka, e le tumelo e e setseng e aname, mme se fa tlhaloso e masalela a ditshidi tse di suleng bogologolo, go le ga ntsi e se nang tsone, jaaka mmala le dipopego tsa tsone.
translated_text:
Setswana: Se ga se supe fela go re, le fa e se mo go kalo, dikgogomodumo dingwe di ne di na le diphuka, e le tumelo e e setseng e aname, mme se fa tlhaloso e masalela a ditshidi tse di suleng bogologolo, go le ga ntsi e se nang tsone, jaaka mmala le dipopego tsa tsone. 
English: Note: While this is not a complete list, it is a good starting point for a discussion of the many unique features of the dinosaurs.

text: Kgogelofatshe ya Io e ka nna jang mo go nna? Fa o ka ema mo Io, bokete ja ga go bo ka nna ko tlase go na le fa o le me Lefatsheng.
translated_text:
Setswana: Kgogelofatshe ya Io e ka nna jang mo go nna? Fa o ka ema mo Io, bokete ja ga go bo ka nna ko tlase go na le fa o le me Lefatsheng. 
English: The answer: The Earth is not flat.

text: NextGen ke thulaganyo e FAA e bolelang fa e tla letla go re difofane di fofe sekgala se sennye mme di somarele dimilione tsa dilithara tsa leokwane ka ngwaga le go fokotsa mosi o kgotlelang.
translated_text:
Setswana: NextGen ke thulaganyo e FAA e bolelang fa e tla letla go re difofane di fofe sekgala se sennye mme di somarele dimilione tsa dilithara tsa leokwane ka ngwaga le go fokotsa mosi o kgotlelang. 
English: NextGen: The FAA says it will allow aircraft to fly shorter routes and save millions of gallons of fuel each year and cut carbon emissions.

text: Tshedimosetso ya tsa neurobiology e naya bosupi jo bo tshwaregang go ditsela tsa megopolo go dira dipatlisiso tsa kitso. Jaanong, e atolosa lefelo la tsa dipatlisiso le go e dira go re e tlhomame go feta.
translated_text:
Setswana: Tshedimosetso ya tsa neurobiology e naya bosupi jo bo tshwaregang go ditsela tsa megopolo go dira dipatlisiso tsa kitso. Jaanong, e atolosa lefelo la tsa dipatlisiso le go e dira go re e tlhomame go feta. 
English: Limitations: The limitations of neurobiological data include the lack of temporal and spatial resolution.

text: Ka nako ya puo ya gagwe ya dioura tse 2, o ne a bolela go re "Gompieno Apple e tlile go nchafatsa mosokelatsebeng. Re tlile go dira ditso gompieno".
translated_text:
Setswana: Ka nako ya puo ya gagwe ya dioura tse 2, o ne a bolela go re "Gompieno Apple e tlile go nchafatsa mosokelatsebeng. Re tlile go dira ditso gompieno". 
English: He added: "Right now, Apple is making a great product. We are working hard to make great products."

text: Mathata a dilense tse di godisang bogolo ke go re go raraana ga pono le palo e e tlhokegang ya dikarolwana tsa dilense go re go fitlhelelwe boleele jo bo farologaneng jwa pono di dikgolo thata go feta tsa dilense tsa pono e e tsepameng.
translated_text:
Setswana: Mathata a dilense tse di godisang bogolo ke go re go raraana ga pono le palo e e tlhokegang ya dikarolwana tsa dilense go re go fitlhelelwe boleele jo bo farologaneng jwa pono di dikgolo thata go feta tsa dilense tsa pono e e tsepameng. 
English: Limitations: The main disadvantage of zoom lenses is that the maximum aperture (the speed) of the lens is usually lower than for prime lenses.

text: Go tshwana le selaola thelebishene, selaodi se dirisa disensara tse pedi tse di beilweng gaufi le modirisi wa thelebishene go kgona go kgaoganya lefelo le mo go lone seraro mo lefelong la boalo jo bo seraro.
translated_text:
Setswana: Go tshwana le selaola thelebishene, selaodi se dirisa disensara tse pedi tse di beilweng gaufi le modirisi wa thelebishene go kgona go kgaoganya lefelo le mo go lone seraro mo lefelong la boalo jo bo seraro. 
English: The technology: The technology is based on two sensors placed near the user's television to triangulate the user's position in three-dimensional space.

text: Baitsaanape ba tsa boranyane ba re diphuka tsa phologolo e, di ne di le bosetlha fa godimo, ko tlase di le borobenyana.
translated_text:
Setswana: Baitsaanape ba tsa boranyane ba re diphuka tsa phologolo e, di ne di le bosetlha fa godimo, ko tlase di le borobenyana. 
English: The result: The animals were grouped into two main groups, the birds and the mammals.

text: Babatlisisi kwa unibesithing e ba kaile go re metswako e mebedi e, fa e amana, e fetoga matlapana a a kgonang go kgoreletsa diphilo go bereka sentle.
translated_text:
Setswana: Babatlisisi kwa unibesithing e ba kaile go re metswako e mebedi e, fa e amana, e fetoga matlapana a a kgonang go kgoreletsa diphilo go bereka sentle. 
English: The two studies found that when two genes are linked, they can act in concert to produce a phenotype.

text: E supegetsa botoka go ka nna gane go feta ya 35mm (3136 mm2 kgatlhanong le 684).
translated_text:
Setswana: E supegetsa botoka go ka nna gane go feta ya 35mm (3136 mm2 kgatlhanong le 684). 
English: Frame: The frame is made of a special alloy that allows it to withstand the high temperatures of the oven (up to 450°C).

text: Ke lebogela ba metlhale ya fibre ya ka fa tlase ga lewatle e kopanyang Europe le disatalaete tsa broadband, lefatshe la Greenland le gokegetswe sentle ka bokete jwa dipercente di le masome a borobabongwe le boraro tsa batho b aba nang le maranyane a internete.
translated_text:
Setswana: Ke lebogela ba metlhale ya fibre ya ka fa tlase ga lewatle e kopanyang Europe le disatalaete tsa broadband, lefatshe la Greenland le gokegetswe sentle ka bokete jwa dipercente di le masome a borobabongwe le boraro tsa batho b aba nang le maranyane a internete. 
English: Internet access: The Internet is available in all settlements, with a high percentage of the population having access to the Internet.

text: Nngwe ya ditiriso tse di tlhageletseng go di gaisa mo setlhopeng seno ke Google Translate, e e go letlang go ranolela o se mo inthanete morago ga go re o laisolole tshedimosetso ya puo e o e batlang.
translated_text:
Setswana: Nngwe ya ditiriso tse di tlhageletseng go di gaisa mo setlhopeng seno ke Google Translate, e e go letlang go ranolela o se mo inthanete morago ga go re o laisolole tshedimosetso ya puo e o e batlang. 
English: Features: One of the most popular apps in this category is Google Translate, which allows you to translate texts after downloading the desired language.

text: A na le sebopego sa dimolekhule se se tshwanang e ka ne e le gase, seeledi, kgotsa a gatsetse.
translated_text:
Setswana: A na le sebopego sa dimolekhule se se tshwanang e ka ne e le gase, seeledi, kgotsa a gatsetse. 
English: Properties: It has the same properties as the gas, liquid, or solid.

text: Tiriso ya go rekote bidio e ile ya lebisa kwa dithibololong tsa botlhokwa mo tlhalosong ya maikutlo a mannye, metsamao ya sefatlhego tse di tsayang sebaka sa disekonto di le dimilione.
translated_text:
Setswana: Tiriso ya go rekote bidio e ile ya lebisa kwa dithibololong tsa botlhokwa mo tlhalosong ya maikutlo a mannye, metsamao ya sefatlhego tse di tsayang sebaka sa disekonto di le dimilione. 
English: The result: A dramatic increase in the number of people watching television, with more than half a billion people now watching TV every day.

text: Batho ba tswa kgakala ba dirisa digalase tsa go bonela koteng dingwaga di le diketekete tse dintsi.
translated_text:
Setswana: Batho ba tswa kgakala ba dirisa digalase tsa go bonela koteng dingwaga di le diketekete tse dintsi. 
English: History: The first camera was invented by a group of early settlers in the 19th century.

text: Masole a ma German, ba ba aparela mariga, le fa bantse ba sitwa ga ba kake ba tlhoka go fenya ntwa.
translated_text:
Setswana: Masole a ma German, ba ba aparela mariga, le fa bantse ba sitwa ga ba kake ba tlhoka go fenya ntwa. 
English: The Germans, who had been defeated, were scattered, and many of their soldiers were killed or captured.

text: Fa go ntse go tsweletse, maotwana a dirilweng ka legong a ne a fetololwa go dirisiwa a tshipi. Ka ngwaga wa 1767, seporo sa ntlha sa ditshipi se ne sa tsenngwa mo tirisong.
translated_text:
Setswana: Fa go ntse go tsweletse, maotwana a dirilweng ka legong a ne a fetololwa go dirisiwa a tshipi. Ka ngwaga wa 1767, seporo sa ntlha sa ditshipi se ne sa tsenngwa mo tirisong. 
English: In 1767, the first steam-powered ship was built.

text: Le fa gone dikarata tse dintsi di siametse go ka letsetsa gongwe le gongwe, tse dingwe di diretswe go neelana ka dielo tse di solegelang molemo tsa go letsa tsa setlhopha se se rileng sa dinaga.
translated_text:

English: Visa requirements: While most countries will not require a visa for visitors of certain countries, some countries will require visitors from certain countries to obtain visas before entering.

text: Bontsi di-telescope tsa dipatlisiso tsa segompieno ke dikago tse di boitshegang mo mafelong a a kgakala a a nang le maemo a atemosefiere a a nametsang.
translated_text:
Setswana: Bontsi di-telescope tsa dipatlisiso tsa segompieno ke dikago tse di boitshegang mo mafelong a a kgakala a a nang le maemo a atemosefiere a a nametsang. 
English: Telescope: A telescope is a large, powerful, and expensive instrument used to study the heavens.

text: Nnale ya tshipi e kokobala mo godimo ga metsi ka ntlha ya kgagamalo ya boalo.
translated_text:
Setswana: Nnale ya tshipi e kokobala mo godimo ga metsi ka ntlha ya kgagamalo ya boalo. 
English: Shape: The blade of a knife is curved.

text: Sebopego sa 35mm tota tota, se ka tsela nngwe se tlhakanyang tlhogo, ke sa bophara jwa 36mm ka boleele jwa 24mm.
translated_text:
Setswana: Sebopego sa 35mm tota tota, se ka tsela nngwe se tlhakanyang tlhogo, ke sa bophara jwa 36mm ka boleele jwa 24mm. 
English: Format: 35mm negative, 36mm negative, 24mm positive

text: Disele tsa mmele ke tsone motheo e bile di botlhokwa thata mo go ithuteng ka botshelo, mo e leng go re ga ntsi di bidiwa "Diagi tsa botshelo".
translated_text:

English: Gene: Gene is the basic unit of all living things and is responsible for the formation of all living things.

text: Batlamedi ba di-VPN (virtual private network) tse di sa tlhakanelwang ke bone ba ba siametseng go dirisiwa fa o batla go tila dikganelelo tse di bewang ke mapolitiki le bagwebi ba ba lekang go bona go re motho yo dirisang enthanete o a bo a le kae.
translated_text:
Setswana: Batlamedi ba di-VPN (virtual private network) tse di sa tlhakanelwang ke bone ba ba siametseng go dirisiwa fa o batla go tila dikganelelo tse di bewang ke mapolitiki le bagwebi ba ba lekang go bona go re motho yo dirisang enthanete o a bo a le kae. 
English: Benefits: VPNs (virtual private network) are not only used for privacy but also for business and political reasons.

text: Ba ne ba se ke ba fetola maitsholo a bone, go fitlhelela ba fetsa motsamao wa bone, le fa ntswa ba ne ba latlhegetswe ke sekaedi go le pele.
translated_text:
Setswana: Ba ne ba se ke ba fetola maitsholo a bone, go fitlhelela ba fetsa motsamao wa bone, le fa ntswa ba ne ba latlhegetswe ke sekaedi go le pele. 
English: The result: They were arrested and charged with trespassing.

text: Batho ba ba nang le tlhaloganyo e ntseng jaana ba akanya sentle, ba kgona go tshwara dilo ka tlhogo ba sa lebale, go rarabolola mathata le go dira ka diteko tsa saense.
translated_text:
Setswana: Batho ba ba nang le tlhaloganyo e ntseng jaana ba akanya sentle, ba kgona go tshwara dilo ka tlhogo ba sa lebale, go rarabolola mathata le go dira ka diteko tsa saense. 
English: These people are intelligent, able to solve problems, and are able to work on scientific tests.

text: Phologolo e e bidiwang ocelot e rata go ja diphologolo tse di nnye. E tshwara ditshwene, dinoga, magotlo le dinonyane. Bontsi ja di phologolo tse di tsongwang ke ocelot di nnye mo go yone.
translated_text:
Setswana: Phologolo e e bidiwang ocelot e rata go ja diphologolo tse di nnye. E tshwara ditshwene, dinoga, magotlo le dinonyane. Bontsi ja di phologolo tse di tsongwang ke ocelot di nnye mo go yone. 
English: Habitat: The ocelot lives in forests, grasslands, and open areas. It will hunt small animals like rabbits, squirrels, snakes, and birds. Most of the ocelots live in small groups.

text: Dikhamera tsa selekanyo se se mo maemong a a fa gare di dirisa selekanyo sa 6cm ka 6cm go tlhomamisa thata e le 56 ka 56mm o o bonalang ka tsela e e farologaneng.
translated_text:
Setswana: Dikhamera tsa selekanyo se se mo maemong a a fa gare di dirisa selekanyo sa 6cm ka 6cm go tlhomamisa thata e le 56 ka 56mm o o bonalang ka tsela e e farologaneng. 
English: Formatting: The most common formats are 6 by 6 cm, 6 by 6 cm negative, and 6 by 6 cm positive.

text: Ba ba sepelang ba gakololwa thata go re ba ele tlhoko diemo tsa loapi tse di ka gomagometsang mafelo a bone ka di ka ama mesepele ya bone.
translated_text:
Setswana: Ba ba sepelang ba gakololwa thata go re ba ele tlhoko diemo tsa loapi tse di ka gomagometsang mafelo a bone ka di ka ama mesepele ya bone. 
English: Travel agents: They are highly recommended for those who are planning to travel abroad.

text: Dibese di tswa mo maemelong a dibese a bokopanelo jwa dikgaolo (go ralala noka) motshegare otlhe, le fa bontsi jwa tsone, segolo jang tse di lebileng kwa bophirima le le Jakar/Bumthang di tswa magareng 06:30 le 07:30.
translated_text:
Setswana: Dibese di tswa mo maemelong a dibese a bokopanelo jwa dikgaolo (go ralala noka) motshegare otlhe, le fa bontsi jwa tsone, segolo jang tse di lebileng kwa bophirima le le Jakar/Bumthang di tswa magareng 06:30 le 07:30. 
English: Departures: Departures from the terminal (in the north) are generally between 06:30 and 07:30.

text: Di tshegetsa mopagami go re a se we mme go ka le matshwenyego a pabalesego ka jaana go kgona go nna thata ya lentswe go ntsha dinao tsa mopagami mo go tsone.
translated_text:
Setswana: Di tshegetsa mopagami go re a se we mme go ka le matshwenyego a pabalesego ka jaana go kgona go nna thata ya lentswe go ntsha dinao tsa mopagami mo go tsone. 
English: The result: The rider loses control of the bike and can become dangerous.

text: Bontsi jwa mesepele ya dikepe tsa Baltic tse di haphegileng di akaretsa go nna kwa St. Petersburg, Russia lobaka.
translated_text:
Setswana: Bontsi jwa mesepele ya dikepe tsa Baltic tse di haphegileng di akaretsa go nna kwa St. Petersburg, Russia lobaka. 
English: St. Petersburg is a major port city in Russia and is a major port city in the Baltic Sea.

text: Go tseelwa go re batsamai ga ba utswe, go tsena fela ba sena tetla, go tsaya karolo mo mmarakeng kwa ntle ga molao, go kopa, kgotsa go tshwara ba bangwe makgwakgwa ka ntlha ya go ipoonela sengwe.
translated_text:
Setswana: Go tseelwa go re batsamai ga ba utswe, go tsena fela ba sena tetla, go tsaya karolo mo mmarakeng kwa ntle ga molao, go kopa, kgotsa go tshwara ba bangwe makgwakgwa ka ntlha ya go ipoonela sengwe. 
English: Warning: Any action taken by a passenger that is not in accordance with these rules may result in the passenger being expelled, without refund, or prosecution.

text: Go na le dilo tse dintsi tse o tshwanetseng go di akanyetsa pele le ka nako ya fa o ya felo gongwe.
translated_text:
Setswana: Go na le dilo tse dintsi tse o tshwanetseng go di akanyetsa pele le ka nako ya fa o ya felo gongwe. 
English: Know what to bring: Here are some things to bring:

text: Mo mogoteng wa letsatsi, basepidi ba ka itemogela meuwane e e dirang go re e nne e kete o bona metsi (kgotsa dilo tse dingwe).
translated_text:
Setswana: Mo mogoteng wa letsatsi, basepidi ba ka itemogela meuwane e e dirang go re e nne e kete o bona metsi (kgotsa dilo tse dingwe). 
English: In the morning, the hikers will have a short walk to get to the water (or other things).

text: Malapa a a nang le bana a ga a tlwaelesega, mme go na le dihosetele tse dingwe tse di kgonang go ba fa boroko mo matlong a a sa kopanelwang.
translated_text:
Setswana: Malapa a a nang le bana a ga a tlwaelesega, mme go na le dihosetele tse dingwe tse di kgonang go ba fa boroko mo matlong a a sa kopanelwang. 
English: Children under the age of 18 are not allowed in the park. Some parks have special rules for children under the age of 18.

text: Sekai ke go etela dikago tsa bogosi ko Loire Valley, le ko Rhine Valley kgotsa go tsaya leoto kwa ditoropong tse di kgatlhisang kwa Danube, kana go tsamaya ka sekepe mo Erie Canal.
translated_text:
Setswana: Sekai ke go etela dikago tsa bogosi ko Loire Valley, le ko Rhine Valley kgotsa go tsaya leoto kwa ditoropong tse di kgatlhisang kwa Danube, kana go tsamaya ka sekepe mo Erie Canal. 
English: Food: Try a visit to a local market, a restaurant, or a traditional German or Austrian pub.

text: Go ka nna botoka go dirisa modiredi yo kgapetsakgapetsa a dirang dipeeletso tse di tshwanang tsa mesepele.
translated_text:
Setswana: Go ka nna botoka go dirisa modiredi yo kgapetsakgapetsa a dirang dipeeletso tse di tshwanang tsa mesepele.

text: Mothale wa Couchsurfing o tlhamilwe ka Hirikgong ka 2004 rramaranyane wa dikhomputara Casey Fenton a sena go bona sefofane sa madi a a kwa tlase go ya Iceland mme a sena kwa a ka bayang tlhogo teng.
translated_text:
Setswana: Mothale wa Couchsurfing o tlhamilwe ka Hirikgong ka 2004 rramaranyane wa dikhomputara Casey Fenton a sena go bona sefofane sa madi a a kwa tlase go ya Iceland mme a sena kwa a ka bayang tlhogo teng. 
English: Couchsurfing was founded in January 2004 by computer programmer Casey Fenton, who wanted to travel to Iceland but was unable to find a flight.

text: Tetlelelo ya baithuti go ya kwa dinageng tse dingwe e nale ditlhokego tse di farologaneng go tsa bajanala kgotsa bo-rrakgwebo
translated_text:
Setswana: Tetlelelo ya baithuti go ya kwa dinageng tse dingwe e nale ditlhokego tse di farologaneng go tsa bajanala kgotsa bo-rrakgwebo 
English: Visa requirements: Different countries have different requirements for students and tourists

text: Lefatshe lengwe le lengwe le na le melao ya lone, ya go re ke didiriswa dife tsa di bewang mo koloing tse di tlhokegang mo maemong a tshoganetso.
translated_text:
Setswana: Lefatshe lengwe le lengwe le na le melao ya lone, ya go re ke didiriswa dife tsa di bewang mo koloing tse di tlhokegang mo maemong a tshoganetso. 
English: Note: Each country has its own laws requiring what items are allowed in the car.

text: Le fa bontsi jwa ditheo di iketleeditse go tsaya bontsi jwa dipeeletso tsa ka metlha, badiredi le bantsi ba ke dikgeleke mo mefuteng e e rileng ya mosepele, madi a a lekanyeditsweng kgotsa mafelo a go jwang kwa go one.
translated_text:
Setswana: Le fa bontsi jwa ditheo di iketleeditse go tsaya bontsi jwa dipeeletso tsa ka metlha, badiredi le bantsi ba ke dikgeleke mo mefuteng e e rileng ya mosepele, madi a a lekanyeditsweng kgotsa mafelo a go jwang kwa go one. 
English: Travel warning: While most of the resorts offer a wide range of amenities, some of them are more expensive for the rich and famous.

text: Bajanala ba kgona go rakana le diphologotswana tse ba sa di tlwaelang kwa ba tswang teng.
translated_text:
Setswana: Bajanala ba kgona go rakana le diphologotswana tse ba sa di tlwaelang kwa ba tswang teng. 
English: Feral: These animals are not confined to their natural habitat.

text: Gape go ela kwa bokone etela Boitshepo jo bogolo jwa Mohumagadi wa Rona Fatima (Tempele), lefelo la lefatshe lotlhe la modimo o o itsegeng Marian.
translated_text:
Setswana: Gape go ela kwa bokone etela Boitshepo jo bogolo jwa Mohumagadi wa Rona Fatima (Tempele), lefelo la lefatshe lotlhe la modimo o o itsegeng Marian. 
English: Also visit the other main tourist attraction of the city, the Cathedral of Our Lady of Fatima (Marian's Tomb).

text: O ka dirisa boda-boda (taxi ya sekuta) go tsamaya mo Goma. Tlhwatlwa ya ka gale (tsa mo gae) ke~500 Congolese Franc fa o tsaya leoto le lekhutshwane.
translated_text:
Setswana: O ka dirisa boda-boda (taxi ya sekuta) go tsamaya mo Goma. Tlhwatlwa ya ka gale (tsa mo gae) ke~500 Congolese Franc fa o tsaya leoto le lekhutshwane. 
English: Breakfast: You can have breakfast in Goma.

text: Go bao ba ratang metshameko ya kwa ntle, tsela ya kwa godimo kwa Lewatleng go ya mankalenkaleng a Loapi e botlhokwa thata.
translated_text:
Setswana: Go bao ba ratang metshameko ya kwa ntle, tsela ya kwa godimo kwa Lewatleng go ya mankalenkaleng a Loapi e botlhokwa thata. 
English: Sports: Swimming, sailing, kayaking, fishing, hunting, and climbing.

text: Safari e e dirwang ka dinao (e gape e bidiwang bush walk, hiking safari kgotsa going "footing") e akaretsa go tsamaya ka dinao lebaka la dioura kgotsa malatsi a le mmalwa.
translated_text:
Setswana: Safari e e dirwang ka dinao (e gape e bidiwang bush walk, hiking safari kgotsa going "footing") e akaretsa go tsamaya ka dinao lebaka la dioura kgotsa malatsi a le mmalwa. 
English: Hiking: Hiking is a form of walking that involves hiking for several days or several weeks.

text: Tsela fela ya go netefatsa go re e feta ka bonako e ne e le go e fetisa jaaka dithoto tse di lebilweng. Melawana ya difofane e ka se letle go romela dithoto kwa ntle ga mopalami, jaanong ke gone fa wena o tsenang teng.
translated_text:
Setswana: Tsela fela ya go netefatsa go re e feta ka bonako e ne e le go e fetisa jaaka dithoto tse di lebilweng. Melawana ya difofane e ka se letle go romela dithoto kwa ntle ga mopalami, jaanong ke gone fa wena o tsenang teng. 
English: Tips: The only way to get a better view of the scenery is to fly over it. The rules of the airline do not allow them to land on the runway.

text: Go tlatsa ka tse 300 go tla oketsa palo yotlhe ya dikara go nna 1300, tse di tla bapalelwang go fokotsa mosuke.
translated_text:
Setswana: Go tlatsa ka tse 300 go tla oketsa palo yotlhe ya dikara go nna 1300, tse di tla bapalelwang go fokotsa mosuke. 
English: The new line will increase capacity by 300% to 1,300 carriages.

text: Malapa a a nang le bana ba ba nnye a ka tlhoka dipaakanyo tse di oketsegileng, mme go nna letsatsi kwa ntle go kgonega motlhofo le e leng ka masea le bana ba khereche.
translated_text:
Setswana: Malapa a a nang le bana ba ba nnye a ka tlhoka dipaakanyo tse di oketsegileng, mme go nna letsatsi kwa ntle go kgonega motlhofo le e leng ka masea le bana ba khereche. 
English: Children: Children under the age of 2 years are not allowed in the park.

text: Mongwe le mongwe yo o tsileng go kgweetsa ko mafelong a a kgakala thata le mola wa Equator, kgotsa kwa godimo ga thaba, o tshwanetse go akanya kgonagalo ya kapoko, serame, kgotsa maemo a bosa a a tsididi thata.
translated_text:
Setswana: Mongwe le mongwe yo o tsileng go kgweetsa ko mafelong a a kgakala thata le mola wa Equator, kgotsa kwa godimo ga thaba, o tshwanetse go akanya kgonagalo ya kapoko, serame, kgotsa maemo a bosa a a tsididi thata. 
English: Weather: Anywhere in the tropics, or in the highlands, you will need to expect high temperatures, hot humid air, or both.

text: Gompieno, Timbuktu ke toropo e e humanegileng, le fa e itsege ka go nna kgogedi ya bajanala, gape e na le boemafofane.
translated_text:
Setswana: Gompieno, Timbuktu ke toropo e e humanegileng, le fa e itsege ka go nna kgogedi ya bajanala, gape e na le boemafofane. 
English: Today, Timbuktu is a city in distress, although it is known as a tourist attraction, and has a airport.

text: Ka dinako tsa diphefo tse di mashetla tse di tlang ka kapoko, kapoko e e seng kana ka sepe e o kgonang go iphitlhela o tlhamile mo go yone e kgona go wa mo sebakeng se se khutshwanyane.
translated_text:
Setswana: Ka dinako tsa diphefo tse di mashetla tse di tlang ka kapoko, kapoko e e seng kana ka sepe e o kgonang go iphitlhela o tlhamile mo go yone e kgona go wa mo sebakeng se se khutshwanyane. 
English: Warning: This article is about the effects of severe weather.

text: Fa o batla go fofa go dikologa Lefatshe lotlhe ka fa Sephatlong sa Borwa fela, maitlhophelo a ga go a difofane le mafelo ga a kalokalo, ka ntlha ya tlhaelo ya ditsela tse di ralalang mawatle.
translated_text:
Setswana: Fa o batla go fofa go dikologa Lefatshe lotlhe ka fa Sephatlong sa Borwa fela, maitlhophelo a ga go a difofane le mafelo ga a kalokalo, ka ntlha ya tlhaelo ya ditsela tse di ralalang mawatle. 
English: Limitations: Flying to South America is not possible without a flight to a South American country, due to the lack of international routes.

text: Difofane tse di tshwanang le bo Emirates, Etihad Airways, Qatar Airways & Turkish Airlines di okeditse ditirelo tsa tsone ko Aforika, e bile di neelana ka dikgokagano go ya ditoropong tse dintsi tse dikgolo tsa Aforika ka ditlhwatlhwa tse di siameng go na le difofane tsa Yuropa.
translated_text:
Setswana: Difofane tse di tshwanang le bo Emirates, Etihad Airways, Qatar Airways & Turkish Airlines di okeditse ditirelo tsa tsone ko Aforika, e bile di neelana ka dikgokagano go ya ditoropong tse dintsi tse dikgolo tsa Aforika ka ditlhwatlhwa tse di siameng go na le difofane tsa Yuropa. 
English: Airlines: Emirates, Etihad Airways, Qatar Airways & Turkish Airlines

text: Ga go dipalangwa dipe tse di oketsegileng tse di tla tsenngwang mme diterena tse di tsamayang mo godimo ga lefatshe ga di kitla di ema kwa Wembley, mme ditirelo tsa go emisa dikoloi le mafelo a go emisa koloi le go e palama ga a yo kwa mabaleng.
translated_text:
Setswana: Ga go dipalangwa dipe tse di oketsegileng tse di tla tsenngwang mme diterena tse di tsamayang mo godimo ga lefatshe ga di kitla di ema kwa Wembley, mme ditirelo tsa go emisa dikoloi le mafelo a go emisa koloi le go e palama ga a yo kwa mabaleng. 
English: Transport: There will be no public transport and trains will not stop at Wembley. Parking: There will be no on-street parking and car parks will not be available near the stadium.

text: Ka kakaretso, fa o batla go nna mo lefatsheng le e seng la gaeno ka lobaka lo lo leele, o tla tshwanela ke go dira lekwalotetla la boagi nako e sale teng.
translated_text:
Setswana: Ka kakaretso, fa o batla go nna mo lefatsheng le e seng la gaeno ka lobaka lo lo leele, o tla tshwanela ke go dira lekwalotetla la boagi nako e sale teng. 
English: Note: If you want to stay in the country for a longer period of time, you will need to obtain a visa.

text: Diterena tsotlhe di na le matoroko a ka bobedi MetroPlus le Metro; a MetroPlus a nna a le ko morago ga terena e e gaufi le Cape Town.
translated_text:
Setswana: Diterena tsotlhe di na le matoroko a ka bobedi MetroPlus le Metro; a MetroPlus a nna a le ko morago ga terena e e gaufi le Cape Town. 
English: MetroRail: All trains have both MetroPlus and Metro; the MetroPlus trains are in the back of the train.

text: Mongwe le mongwe o na le seabe mo sechabeng mme botlhe ba dirisa dipagamo tsa sechaba. Bontsi jwa batho ba ngongoregela dipagamo tsa sechaba.
translated_text:
Setswana: Mongwe le mongwe o na le seabe mo sechabeng mme botlhe ba dirisa dipagamo tsa sechaba. Bontsi jwa batho ba ngongoregela dipagamo tsa sechaba. 
English: Transportation: Everyone in the country uses public transport. Most people use public transport.

text: Ka mafelo a se na baagi ba bantsi le kgotlelego e le kwa tlase, ka jalo e se bothata ka metlha, gape o tlile go itumelela dinaledi.
translated_text:
Setswana: Ka mafelo a se na baagi ba bantsi le kgotlelego e le kwa tlase, ka jalo e se bothata ka metlha, gape o tlile go itumelela dinaledi. 
English: Note: There are few places in the world with more variety of wildlife and more beautiful scenery than in this area.

text: Melawana le madi a dipampiri tsa teseletso ya mosepele tsa Visa di farologana ka mafatshe e bile e laolwa ke lefatshe le o tlholegang kwa go lone.
translated_text:
Setswana: Melawana le madi a dipampiri tsa teseletso ya mosepele tsa Visa di farologana ka mafatshe e bile e laolwa ke lefatshe le o tlholegang kwa go lone. 
English: Note: The fees and requirements for visas can vary from country to country and are subject to change without notice.

text: Fa re buwa fela, ga gona mosola wa go re o leke go fokolediwa tlhwatlhwa fa o le mo karolong ya kgwebo, kgotsa ya maemo a ntlha, mo sefofaneng se se tlhamalelang go tswa lefelo A go ya B.
translated_text:
Setswana: Fa re buwa fela, ga gona mosola wa go re o leke go fokolediwa tlhwatlhwa fa o le mo karolong ya kgwebo, kgotsa ya maemo a ntlha, mo sefofaneng se se tlhamalelang go tswa lefelo A go ya B. 
English: Note: There is no direct flight from A to B.

text: Go latlhela Boomerang ke bokgoni jo bo rategang jo baeti ba le bantsi ba ka ratang go nna le jone.
translated_text:
Setswana: Go latlhela Boomerang ke bokgoni jo bo rategang jo baeti ba le bantsi ba ka ratang go nna le jone. 
English: Tip: Try to land the boomerang in the air.

text: O ka nna wa se dirise sefofane se fa o sa batle go ralala mafelo a a kwa borwa jwa lewatle la Pacific le a a mo letshitshing le le kwa bophirima ba Amerika o o borwa.(bona kwa tlase)
translated_text:
Setswana: O ka nna wa se dirise sefofane se fa o sa batle go ralala mafelo a a kwa borwa jwa lewatle la Pacific le a a mo letshitshing le le kwa bophirima ba Amerika o o borwa.(bona kwa tlase) 
English: Note: You will not be able to fly into the US or Canada from this airport.

text: San Francisco e tlhomile mafaratlhatlha a magolo a bojanala a a akaretsang dihotele di le mmalwa, mafelo a dijo mmogo le mafelo a maemo a a kwa godimo a go tshwarelwang diphuthego mo one.
translated_text:
Setswana: San Francisco e tlhomile mafaratlhatlha a magolo a bojanala a a akaretsang dihotele di le mmalwa, mafelo a dijo mmogo le mafelo a maemo a a kwa godimo a go tshwarelwang diphuthego mo one. 
English: San Francisco has developed a large tourist infrastructure with numerous hotels, restaurants, and top-notch convention facilities.

text: Go ithaopa o le mo maetong ke motlhale o mongwe o mw ntle ya go dira pharologanyo; mme ga se ka go aba fela.
translated_text:
Setswana: Go ithaopa o le mo maetong ke motlhale o mongwe o mw ntle ya go dira pharologanyo; mme ga se ka go aba fela. 
English: Be aware: this is a dangerous activity and should only be done by a professional.

text: Batho ba ka nna ba se lebelele go re boitshoko le go tlhaloganya le tsone di botlhokwa mo batsamaing ba ba boelang gae.
translated_text:
Setswana: Batho ba ka nna ba se lebelele go re boitshoko le go tlhaloganya le tsone di botlhokwa mo batsamaing ba ba boelang gae. 
English: Note: People may not be ready to accept this new language and culture.

text: O seka wa lebala go tsenyeletsa ditshenyegelelo tse di okeditsweng ke dibukana tse dingwe tsa mesepele, makgetho a mesepele, sepalamo jalo jalo. gotlhe ko go etelwang teng ko ntle ga Afrika.
translated_text:
Setswana: O seka wa lebala go tsenyeletsa ditshenyegelelo tse di okeditsweng ke dibukana tse dingwe tsa mesepele, makgetho a mesepele, sepalamo jalo jalo. gotlhe ko go etelwang teng ko ntle ga Afrika. 
English: Note: This itinerary is not a complete list of all possible activities in South Africa. It is just a rough guide.

text: Baagi ba le mmalwa ba Bishbek ba ne ba pega badiraditshupetso ba ba tswang kwa borwa molato ka ntlha ya botlhokatsebe jwa bone.
translated_text:
Setswana: Baagi ba le mmalwa ba Bishbek ba ne ba pega badiraditshupetso ba ba tswang kwa borwa molato ka ntlha ya botlhokatsebe jwa bone. 
English: Protesters: Several Bishkek residents protested outside the court.

text: Dikarolo tsa segompieno tsa Belgium e ne e le karolo ya Luxembourg mo nakong e e fetileng mme ya nna karolo ya Belgium morago ga Phetogo ya kwa Belgium ya bo-1830.
translated_text:
Setswana: Dikarolo tsa segompieno tsa Belgium e ne e le karolo ya Luxembourg mo nakong e e fetileng mme ya nna karolo ya Belgium morago ga Phetogo ya kwa Belgium ya bo-1830. 
English: Belgium: The present-day Belgian part of Belgium was part of Luxembourg in the past and was Belgian after the 1830s Belgian Revolution.

text: Fa e sale ka ngwaga wa 1988, go dirisiwa mabokoso a matlhopel a, a bonatsang, go re batlhophi ba kgone go bona go re ga go na ditlhopho dipe tse di tsentsweng pele go simololwa, le go re ga go tsennwe ditlhopho dipe ntleng ga tsa batlhophi ba ba rebotsweng ka fa tsamaisong
translated_text:
Setswana: Fa e sale ka ngwaga wa 1988, go dirisiwa mabokoso a matlhopel a, a bonatsang, go re batlhophi ba kgone go bona go re ga go na ditlhopho dipe tse di tsentsweng pele go simololwa, le go re ga go tsennwe ditlhopho dipe ntleng ga tsa batlhophi ba ba rebotsweng ka fa tsamaisong 
English: Since 1988, ballot boxes have been installed at polling stations to ensure that voters can see that no envelopes are left unattended prior to the start of voting, and that no envelopes are left unattended during the voting process.

text: Tonakgolo wa nama-o-sa-tshwere, Julia Gillard o buile ka ipapatso ya ditlhopo tsa puso-kgolo tsa 2010 go re o dumela go re Australia e tshwanetse e nne puso ya rephaboliki fa paka ya ga Mmamosadinyana (Elizabeth II) e wela.
translated_text:
Setswana: Tonakgolo wa nama-o-sa-tshwere, Julia Gillard o buile ka ipapatso ya ditlhopo tsa puso-kgolo tsa 2010 go re o dumela go re Australia e tshwanetse e nne puso ya rephaboliki fa paka ya ga Mmamosadinyana (Elizabeth II) e wela. 
English: Prime Minister: Julia Gillard

text: Puso ya ma-Irish e gatelela go potlaka ga melao ya palamente go baakanya seemo.
translated_text:
Setswana: Puso ya ma-Irish e gatelela go potlaka ga melao ya palamente go baakanya seemo. 
English: The Irish government is trying to block the legislation.

text: Dingangisano tsa sepolitiki kaga kgaolo di tsweletse ka go goga goga mo seretseng dikamano tsa magareng ga Armenia le Azerbaijan.
translated_text:
Setswana: Dingangisano tsa sepolitiki kaga kgaolo di tsweletse ka go goga goga mo seretseng dikamano tsa magareng ga Armenia le Azerbaijan. 
English: Geopolitical situation: The conflict is between Armenia and Azerbaijan.

text: Tonakgolo, Rre Stephen Harper o dumetse go romela molawana wa ”Clean Air Act” wa puso kwa malokong otlhe a komiti go sekasekwa pele ga e balwa la bobedi; morago ga bokopano ja metsotso e le masome a mabedi le botlhano le moetapele wa NDP, Jack Layton, kwa PMO ka Labobedi.
translated_text:
Setswana: Tonakgolo, Rre Stephen Harper o dumetse go romela molawana wa ”Clean Air Act” wa puso kwa malokong otlhe a komiti go sekasekwa pele ga e balwa la bobedi; morago ga bokopano ja metsotso e le masome a mabedi le botlhano le moetapele wa NDP, Jack Layton, kwa PMO ka Labobedi. 
English: The PMO meeting was held on Tuesday afternoon, after the NDP leader Jack Layton tabled a motion to have the PMO review the Clean Air Act.

text: Mo kgweding e e fitileng go ne go na le bangongoregi ko Poland fa lefatshe leo le dumelana ka mokwalo le ACTA, se se ne sa gogela ko go reng puso ya Poland e tseye tshweetso go sa baakanya tumelano le gompieno.

text: Le fa go ntse jalo, dithulaganyo tseno di ne tsa tlhoka mosola ka bonako fela fa masole a ka nna 800,000 a Seseole se se Hibidu sa Soviet Union a tsena, se dira thibelelo kwa Belarus le Ukraine, morago ga go tsenelela karolo e e botlhaba ba lefatshe la Poland, ba tsuolola ditumalano tsa Riga Peace Treaty, Soviet- Polish Non Aggression Pact, le melawana e mengwe e go dumalanweng ka yona gareng ga bone fela le gareng ga mafatshe a mangwe.
translated_text:
Setswana: Le fa go ntse jalo, dithulaganyo tseno di ne tsa tlhoka mosola ka bonako fela fa masole a ka nna 800,000 a Seseole se se Hibidu sa Soviet Union a tsena, se dira thibelelo kwa Belarus le Ukraine, morago ga go tsenelela karolo e e botlhaba ba lefatshe la Poland, ba tsuolola ditumalano tsa Riga Peace Treaty, Soviet- Polish Non Aggression Pact, le melawana e mengwe e go dumalanweng ka yona gareng ga bone fela le gareng ga mafatshe a mangwe. 
English: However, these agreements were not implemented immediately, as the Soviet Union withdrew from the country, and the Belarussian and Ukrainian fronts were opened, and the Polish front was also opened, and the Riga Peace Treaty, Soviet-Polish Non-Agression Pact, and other agreements were signed between the Soviet Union and other countries.

text: Manokonoko a go itshosa thata, e seng khutsafalo kgotsa letshogo le le tlwaelesegileng, ke one a a neng a bakwa ke bokopano ja beke le beke jwa PA
translated_text:

text: Go nna le dikoloi di le dintsi go baka dikotsi di le dintsi mo tseleng, se se dira dithunamiso tse disha mo go tsa botsogo go baakanya mebele e e senyegileng.

English: Roads: The roads are very bad in the country, so the new cars are not able to reach the places where the old ones are.

text: Badira dipatlisiso ba tlhalosa fa se se tla thusa go tshwara kankere, bolwetse jwa kgotlholo e tona, HIV, le letshoroma go sale gale, mo balwetseng ba ba mo mafatsheng a a humanegileng; ko selekanyetso sa go fola mo malwetsing a a tshwanang le kankere ya mabele se ka nna sephatlo sa kwa mafatsheng a a tlhabologileng.
translated_text:
Setswana: Badira dipatlisiso ba tlhalosa fa se se tla thusa go tshwara kankere, bolwetse jwa kgotlholo e tona, HIV, le letshoroma go sale gale, mo balwetseng ba ba mo mafatsheng a a humanegileng; ko selekanyetso sa go fola mo malwetsing a a tshwanang le kankere ya mabele se ka nna sephatlo sa kwa mafatsheng a a tlhabologileng. 
English: The study also found that the risk of dying from breast cancer, HIV, tuberculosis and malaria was reduced by half in countries with a high level of education.

text: Dr. Ehud Ur, morutuntshi wa tsa bongaka kwa Yunibesiting ya Dalhousie kwa Halifax, Nova Scotia, yo gape e leng modulasetilo lekalana la tsa kalafi le maranyane la Mokgatlho wa Canada wa Bolwetse jwa Sukiri, o tsibositse go re dipatlisiso tse di sentse e le gone di simolodisiwang.
translated_text:

English: Dr. Ehud Ur, a professor of medicine at Dalhousie University in Halifax, Nova Scotia, and a member of the Canadian Diabetes Association's clinical and scientific committee, said the results of the study were promising.

English: Children are taught to “be nice to other children”, to “play nicely with other children”, and to “be polite to other people”.

text: Badiredi ba toropo ya Amsterdam le motlobo wa ditso wa Anne Frank, ba re fa setlhare se amilwe ke thuthuntshwane ya lekwati, seo ke matshosetsi mo boitekanelo jwa botsogo jwa sechaba, ba ngangisanya go re se ka baka kotsi ya dikgobalo tse di masisi fa se wa.

Setswana: Enceladus ke karolo e e bonalang thata ya thulaganyo ya masedi, e bontsha mo e ka nnang diperesente di le 90 tsa marang a letsatsi a a le itayang. 
English: Enceladus is the most reflective object in the solar system.

text: Ga go sepe se se ka bonwang fa e se bophepa fela, loapi lo lo ntle kwa godimo le dithaba tse di mo tikologong. Ke go le gonnye fela go go ka bonwang mo lefatsheng leno kgotsa ga utlwiwa go tswa mo teng ga logaga lono.
translated_text:
Setswana: Ga go sepe se se ka bonwang fa e se bophepa fela, loapi lo lo ntle kwa godimo le dithaba tse di mo tikologong. Ke go le gonnye fela go go ka bonwang mo lefatsheng leno kgotsa ga utlwiwa go tswa mo teng ga logaga lono. 
English: Scenery: Nothing can be seen but the mountains and the clouds above. This is the only place on Earth that can be seen from space.

text: Jaanong re bua ka lefatshe la Japane. Lefatshe la Japane e ne e le setlhaketlhake fela jaaka Borithane.
translated_text:
Setswana: Jaanong re bua ka lefatshe la Japane. Lefatshe la Japane e ne e le setlhaketlhake fela jaaka Borithane. 
English: Japan: Japan is a country. Japan is a country.

text: Fa se le ko setlhoweng, Setsuwatsuwe wa Gonu, se se teilweng ka kgetse ya matlhare a sethare sa di-palms mo puong ya se-Maldives, se ne se le diphefo tse di tsamayang ka lebelo la dikhilomithara di le 240 ka oura (dimmaele tse149 ka oura).
translated_text:
Setswana: Fa se le ko setlhoweng, Setsuwatsuwe wa Gonu, se se teilweng ka kgetse ya matlhare a sethare sa di-palms mo puong ya se-Maldives, se ne se le diphefo tse di tsamayang ka lebelo la dikhilomithara di le 240 ka oura (dimmaele tse149 ka oura). 
English: Gonu, the second-highest storm on the Saffir-Simpson Hurricane Scale, was named for the Maldives.

text: Lefelo la Turkey, go akaretsa le matsha, le disekwere khilomithara di le 783,562 (300,948 sq mi), tse mo go tsone disekwere khilomithara di le 755,688 (291,773 sq mi) di leng kwa borwa-bophirima jwa Asia le disekwere khilomithara di le 23,764 (9,174 sq mi) di leng kwa Yuropa.
translated_text:
Setswana: Lefelo la Turkey, go akaretsa le matsha, le disekwere khilomithara di le 783,562 (300,948 sq mi), tse mo go tsone disekwere khilomithara di le 755,688 (291,773 sq mi) di leng kwa borwa-bophirima jwa Asia le disekwere khilomithara di le 23,764 (9,174 sq mi) di leng kwa Yuropa. 
English: Turkey

text: Ditlhaketlhake tsa Borwa jwa Shetland, bo lemogilwe ka 1819, bontsi jwa ditšhaba tse di farologaneng bo ile jwa re bolela fa ele ditlhaketlhake jwa tsone le gore di na le motheo o montsi, tse lesome le borataro ka 2020.
translated_text:
Setswana: Ditlhaketlhake tsa Borwa jwa Shetland, bo lemogilwe ka 1819, bontsi jwa ditšhaba tse di farologaneng bo ile jwa re bolela fa ele ditlhaketlhake jwa tsone le gore di na le motheo o montsi, tse lesome le borataro ka 2020. 
English: South Shetland Islands, discovered in 1819, are claimed by several nations and have the most bases, with ten active in 2020.

text: Apia ke motsemoshate wa Samoa. Toropo eno e mo setlhaketlhakeng sa Upolu mme e na le baagi ba ba kwa tlasenyana fela ga 40,000.
translated_text:
Setswana: Apia ke motsemoshate wa Samoa. Toropo eno e mo setlhaketlhakeng sa Upolu mme e na le baagi ba ba kwa tlasenyana fela ga 40,000. 
English: Capital: Apia

text: E re ka setsuatsue se le kgakala le go goroga mo lefatsheng, ga go bonolo go ka sekaseka go re ditlamorago tsa sone di tla nna jang mo lefatsheng la Amerika kgotsa kwa Caribbean.
translated_text:
Setswana: E re ka setsuatsue se le kgakala le go goroga mo lefatsheng, ga go bonolo go ka sekaseka go re ditlamorago tsa sone di tla nna jang mo lefatsheng la Amerika kgotsa kwa Caribbean. 
English: Warning: This article is about hurricanes. For tropical storms, see Storm

text: Le le sesane fa tlase ga mawatle, la bo le nna lekimanyana fa tlase ga dithota.
translated_text:
Setswana: Le le sesane fa tlase ga mawatle, la bo le nna lekimanyana fa tlase ga dithota. 
English: Color: It is a light yellow in color.

text: Dikgwa tse ga se mafelo a loraga a a tletseng metsi fela, go na le mafelo a kileng a bo a aperwe ke dikgwa tse di tona tse di kitlameng, tse di tala.
translated_text:
Setswana: Dikgwa tse ga se mafelo a loraga a a tletseng metsi fela, go na le mafelo a kileng a bo a aperwe ke dikgwa tse di tona tse di kitlameng, tse di tala. 
English: Tags: There are no specific hiking trails here, but there are several popular trails that start at the base of the mountain.

text: Mmepe wa mafatshefatshe ka thoromo ya lefatshe ka ba lephata la badupi ba tshekatsheko ya popego ya lefatshe ke ba United States, o supile go re ga go a nna le thoromo ya lefatshe mo Iceland beke pele ga moo.
translated_text:
Setswana: Mmepe wa mafatshefatshe ka thoromo ya lefatshe ka ba lephata la badupi ba tshekatsheko ya popego ya lefatshe ke ba United States, o supile go re ga go a nna le thoromo ya lefatshe mo Iceland beke pele ga moo. 
English: The United States Geological Survey: There was no earthquake in Iceland in the week prior to the USGS report.

text: Ke iketlile mo godimo ga nngwe ya dithaba kwa Bokone jwa Mecca, logaga lono lo ikemetse kwa thoko fela lo le nosi mo lefatsheng lotlhe.
translated_text:
Setswana: Ke iketlile mo godimo ga nngwe ya dithaba kwa Bokone jwa Mecca, logaga lono lo ikemetse kwa thoko fela lo le nosi mo lefatsheng lotlhe. 
English: Topic: The highest mountain in the world
